  "prompt": "What would be the best attire for me?",
  "response": "To provide the best recommendation for your attire, I'll need more information about the occasion, your personal style, and any specific preferences you might have. Here are some general suggestions based on different scenarios:\n\n### Casual Day Out\n- **Men**: A well-fitted t-shirt or polo shirt paired with jeans or chinos. Sneakers or casual shoes.\n- **Women**: A comfortable top or blouse with jeans, leggings, or a casual skirt. Sandals or sneakers.\n\n### Business Casual\n- **Men**: A button-up shirt with chinos or dress pants. Loafers or dress shoes.\n- **Women**: A blouse or a neat top with dress pants, a skirt, or dressy jeans. Flats or low heels.\n\n### Formal Event\n- **Men**: A suit and tie, preferably in dark colors like navy or black. Dress shoes.\n- **Women**: A cocktail dress or an elegant pantsuit. Heels or dressy flats.\n\n### Outdoor Activities\n- **Men and Women**: Moisture-wicking tops and quick-dry pants or shorts. Comfortable, supportive shoes like hiking boots or sneakers.\n\n### Special Considerations\n- **Weather**: If it's cold, layer with a jacket or sweater. If it's hot, opt for breathable fabrics like cotton or linen.\n- **Cultural Sensitivity**: Be aware of local customs and dress codes, especially when traveling.\n\nIf you can provide more details about the specific occasion or your personal style, I can offer more tailored advice!",
